% vm-starve.trx -- leak heap at save level 0 until the VM is exhausted.
% At exhaustion the global handler cannot allocate its stack-preservation
% arrays either, so it takes the 'insufficient VM for vm-full handler'
% short-circuit.  That abnormal exit must carry +Error::VMFull (45) as
% the process exit code, not 0 (ENGINE BUG #9); run_cli_tests.sh pins it.
{ 4096 string pop } loop
(unreachable) =
